OL,3,CSeven men jailed for 'sophisticated'
OL,4,C#250 million drug conspiracy
OL,6,FSeven men charged in connection to a
OL,7,F"sophisticated and organised"
OL,8,Foperation to bring Class A drugs into
OL,9,Fthe UK have been put behind bars for
OL,10,Fmore than 50 years in total.
OL,12,FThe importation of two tonnes of Class
OL,13,FA drugs, with an estimated street
OL,14,Fvalue of more than #250 million
OL,15,Fpounds, was uncovered as part of an
OL,16,Foperation by North West Regional
OL,17,FOrganised Crime Unit (NWROCU).
