OL,3,CSeven men jailed for 'sophisticated'
OL,4,C#250 million drug conspiracy
OL,6,FSitting at Mold Crown Court, Judge
OL,7,FRhys Rowlands told the defendants the
OL,8,Fquantities of drugs involved in this
OL,9,Foperation were "vast", believed to be
OL,10,F"several hundred kilograms" and beyond
OL,11,Fwhat is normally dealt with at the
OL,12,Fcourt.
OL,14,FThe drugs, distributed from a north
OL,15,FWales farm, would have "ended up sold
OL,16,Fon the streets causing problems for
OL,17,Fthose addicted and society at large,"
OL,18,Fsaid Judge Rowlands.
