OL,3,CSeven men jailed for 'sophisticated'
OL,4,C#250 million drug conspiracy
OL,6,FPretty much everyone involved in this
OL,7,Fcase was making "very large amounts of
OL,8,Fmoney," said Judge Rowlands and he
OL,9,Fadded "the crimes were born out of
OL,10,Ffunding a lifestyle or financial
OL,11,Freward".
OL,13,FSeven men and two women were facing
OL,14,Fsentencing today. They had all
OL,15,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to the
OL,16,Fcharges against them.
OL,18,FThe wider criminal network saw drugs
OL,19,Ftransported from Holland, France and
OL,20,FBelgium into the UK via the Eurotunnel.
