OL,6,FAn empty trailer was used to conceal
OL,7,Fthe drugs and once in the UK, they
OL,8,Fwere moved to a disused farm in
OL,9,FAlltami near Mold in North Wales which
OL,10,Fwas used as a distribution hub.
OL,12,FThe drugs were repackaged and
OL,13,Fdistributed to couriers across the
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FTirglas farm in Flintshire is in close
OL,17,Fproximity to the A55 and Liverpool and
OL,18,FManchester.
