OL,4,C#250 million drug conspiracy
OL,6,FJudge Rhys Rowlands told the court "At
OL,7,Fthe heart of this case was a well
OL,8,Forganised and sophisticated operation
OL,9,Fto bring Class A drugs into this
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,F"The operation involved those buying
OL,13,For selling drugs either on or near the
OL,14,FA55."
OL,16,FThe crimes came to light after an
OL,17,Finvestigation known as Operation
OL,18,FFalcon involving police from a number
OL,19,Fof force areas. The Flintshire farm
OL,20,Fwas raided in September last year.
