OL,6,FEarlier this year, four others
OL,7,Freceived a combined sentence for their
OL,8,Frole in the smuggling.
OL,10,FToday at Mold Crown Court lengthy
OL,11,Fsentences were handed down for those
OL,12,Finvolved.
OL,14,FIt was said in court that Mark Blower
OL,15,Fplayed a leading role in the
OL,16,Foperation. The London supplier was
OL,17,Fsentenced to 14 years and 3 months for
OL,18,Fconspiracy to supply Class A drugs.
