OL,6,FJon Fairclough was involved in
OL,7,Ftransporting large quantities of
OL,8,Fdrugs. The courier made six drugs runs
OL,9,Fto the farm although he never went on
OL,10,Fsite and would meet elsewhere. He
OL,11,Fdistributed the drugs across the
OL,12,FLiverpool area and was jailed for 7
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FMichael Day, another courier who
OL,16,Fvisited the farm, was sentenced to 6
OL,17,Fyears.
