OL,3,CSeven men jailed for 'sophisticated'
OL,4,C#250 million drug conspiracy
OL,6,F50 year old David Hague was accused of
OL,7,Ftransporting large quantities of Class
OL,8,FA drugs to Yorkshire. He visited the
OL,9,Ffarm eight times and was sentenced to
OL,10,F9 years and 4 months.
OL,12,FJamie Menagh had a leading role in the
OL,13,Foperation, helping the group
OL,14,Fdistribute drugs to other couriers who
OL,15,Fvisited the farm. He was spotted on
OL,16,Fthe farm's CCTV loading drugs into his
OL,17,Fvan and was sent to prison for 7 years
OL,18,Fand 6 months.
