OL,3,CSeven men jailed for 'sophisticated'
OL,4,C#250 million drug conspiracy
OL,6,FIn the dock today were sisters Alesha
OL,7,FLee and Erin Lee. They sat alongside
OL,8,FMichael Hardie and all three pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to perverting the course of
OL,10,Fjustice. They had gone to the farm on
OL,11,Fthe day of the raid and were spotted
OL,12,Fby police in the area. They made a 999
OL,13,Fcall where they claimed to have been
OL,14,Fkidnapped at knifepoint.
OL,16,FHardie was accused of deliberately
OL,17,Fmisleading the police and told he
OL,18,Fwould have known how serious his
OL,19,Fbehaviour was. He was sent to jail for
OL,20,F12 months.
