OL,3,CSeven men jailed for 'sophisticated'
OL,4,C#250 million drug conspiracy
OL,6,FAlesha and Erin Lee who cried
OL,7,Fthroughout the sentencing, received 8
OL,8,Fmonths suspended sentences for 18
OL,9,Fmonths. The young mothers were
OL,10,Finconsolable as they left the dock.
OL,12,FCharles Dilworth fled the scene and
OL,13,Fleft the country during the warrant.
OL,14,FHe was arrested at Manchester airport
OL,15,Fon his return and received 7 years and
OL,16,F6 months for conspiracy to supply
OL,17,FClass A drugs.
