OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Ian
OL,7,FWhitehead, Head of the NWROCU said:
OL,8,F"This operation demonstrates our
OL,9,Funwavering commitment to dismantling
OL,10,Forganised crime networks and
OL,11,Fprotecting our communities from the
OL,12,Fscourge of illegal drugs.
OL,14,F"This brings the total to over 100
OL,15,Fyears sentencing for Operation Falcon.
OL,17,F"We will continue to work tirelessly
OL,18,Fto bring those involved in drug
OL,19,Ftrafficking to justice and ensure the
OL,20,Fsafety of the communities in the North
OL,21,FWest."
